<h1>DRAFT - FreeBMD Progress</h1>

<p class="lead"> FreeBMD is an [on-going project] [link="Frequently Asked Questions About FreeBMD#1"], whose aims are to transcribe the Civil Registration index of births, marriages and deaths for England and Wales; and, at present the whole index has not yet been transcribed. The project started with the oldest records, from July 1873, and is moving forward simultaneously on births, marriages and deaths up to the end of 1992. Some of the newest records may be either incompletely transcribed, or not yet started and there may be gaps or “holes” in their coverage.</p>

 <h2> Coverage of FreeBMD records to date</h2>
